    </note>Katika safari yote ya Waisraeli, kila wakati wingu lilipoinuka kutoka juu ya Maskani ya Mungu, wangeondoka; <verse eid="EXO 40:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 40:37"/>lakini kama wingu halikuinuka, hawakuondoka, mpaka siku lilipoinuka. <verse eid="EXO 40:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 40:38"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">40:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 9:15">Hes 9:15</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 13:21">Kut 13:21</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 10:1">1Kor 10:1</ref></char></note>Kwa hiyo wingu la <char style="nd">Bwana</char> lilikuwa juu ya maskani mchana, na moto ulikuwa katika hilo wingu wakati wa usiku, machoni pa nyumba yote ya Israeli siku zote za safari zao.<verse eid="EXO 40:38"/></para>
